item.title: Watch astonishing moment Starship booster caught in mid-air 'chopsticks manoeuvre'
item.description: It’s the first time the "chopsticks manoeuvre" has been attempted, with previous boosters landing in the ocean.

item.title: Watch: In A First, SpaceX 'Catches' Falling Rocket Booster On Launchpad
item.description: SpaceX successfully "caught" the first-stage booster of its Starship megarocket Sunday as it returned to the launch pad after a test flight, a world first in the company's quest for rapid reusability.
